graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Control Plane"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Reconciles CRDs]
        Webhook[kserve-webhook-server<br/>Validates & Mutates<br/>Port: 9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates resources| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceService[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        ServingRuntime[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceGraph[InferenceGraph CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModel[TrainedModel CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "KServe Data Plane"
        direction TB
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Init Container<br/>Downloads Models]
        ModelServer[Model Server Runtimes<br/>sklearn/xgboost/pytorch/tensorflow/etc<br/>Port: 8080/TCP]
        Agent[kserve-agent<br/>Sidecar: Logging/Batching]
        Router[kserve-router<br/>Multi-step Inference Graphs]
        Explainer[Explainer Servers<br/>Alibi/ART]

        StorageInit -->|loads artifacts| ModelServer
        Agent -->|wraps requests| ModelServer
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>VirtualService/Gateway]
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>Serverless/Autoscaling]
        Storage[S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies"
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>mTLS/Traffic Routing]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Authentication]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Management]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Metadata/Versioning]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| InferenceService
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages| InferenceService

    InferenceService -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceGraph -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModel -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService[Knative Service]
    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Kubernetes Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService]

    Controller -->|depends on| Knative
    Controller -->|depends on| Istio
    Controller -->|integrates with| ModelRegistry

    StorageInit -->|downloads from| Storage

    ModelServer -->|protected by| ServiceMesh
    ModelServer -->|authenticated via| OAuth

    Router -->|orchestrates| InferenceGraph
    Router -->|calls multiple| ModelServer

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceService fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style StorageInit fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelRegistry fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
